column5: About those musky spots you had on your gps.
hahah I see your luck is as good as mine! Maybe you need a bigger bait. Glad to see you are getting out at least

...oh and remember, one of those waypoints is actually a rock, not a musky location. I'm too electronically challenged to label them. Hope you don't find that one (its on Head Lake in case you forgot)
Totally off topic.  I saw this post, and thought of my "new to me" musky rod.....  Paid $10 for it!!  With the reel...  This MUST be the same Rizzo!!  Right?
wow $10? I'll give you 15 (it has my name on it after all). Actually the Rizzo is after Frank Rizzo...R I Z Z O of jerky boys fame
